1000
01:22:10,828 --> 01:22:13,004
<i>"Dong Hyeon, ľúbim ťa."</i>

1001
01:22:14,665 --> 01:22:15,999
Čo tu robíš?

1002
01:22:18,261 --> 01:22:21,263
Čo chcela Yoon Ji?

1003
01:22:22,573 --> 01:22:24,166
Nič.

1004
01:22:24,166 --> 01:22:26,734
Vyznala ti svoje city?

1005
01:22:28,312 --> 01:22:29,604
Nie, to nie.

1006
01:22:29,604 --> 01:22:31,900
Budeš s ňou chodiť?

1007
01:22:33,615 --> 01:22:36,111
Išla by si do väzenia,
keby si mala po štyridsiatke?

1008
01:22:36,111 --> 01:22:39,306
Po štyridsiatke?
Kto?

1009
01:22:40,857 --> 01:22:44,036
To je jedno.
Nebudem s ňou chodiť.

1010
01:22:44,036 --> 01:22:45,027
Tak začni chodiť so mnou.

1011
01:22:45,028 --> 01:22:46,321
Hej!

1012
01:22:46,321 --> 01:22:48,857
Nepáčim sa ti?

1013
01:22:48,857 --> 01:22:51,401
