1016
01:23:00,594 --> 01:23:03,996
Komu si vyznala svoje city?

1017
01:23:03,996 --> 01:23:06,182
Dong Hyeonovi.

1018
01:23:06,182 --> 01:23:08,676
Veď aj ty ho máš rada.

1019
01:23:10,729 --> 01:23:12,272
Zbláznila si sa?!

1020
01:23:12,272 --> 01:23:16,059
Nie! Nikdy!
Ani za milión rokov!

1021
01:23:16,059 --> 01:23:18,336
