takže na to ani nepomysli!

1022
01:23:18,336 --> 01:23:21,398
To on ma zachránil na tej párty!

1023
01:23:21,398 --> 01:23:24,158
Riskoval kvôli mne svoj život!

1024
01:23:24,158 --> 01:23:26,343
Hyeon Jeong.

1025
01:23:26,343 --> 01:23:28,055
Hyeon Jeong, prosím ťa.

1026
01:23:28,055 --> 01:23:31,266
Počúvaj ma.
Toto je zlé.

1027
01:23:31,266 --> 01:23:33,543
Daj mi nejaký normálny dôvod.

1028
01:23:33,543 --> 01:23:36,438
Stará sa o mňa a má ma rád,
ako vlastný otec.

1029
01:23:36,438 --> 01:23:38,515
Veď to!

1030
01:23:38,515 --> 01:23:41,392
