1040
01:24:34,145 --> 01:24:39,442
Čo mám urobiť, aby si mi odpustila?

1041
01:24:43,697 --> 01:24:48,875
Keby som to vedela,
už by som ti to dávno povedala.

1042
01:24:48,875 --> 01:24:55,792
Aj keby som ti odpustila,
bola by to iba aféra, alebo si zabudol?

1043
01:24:58,103 --> 01:25:00,012
Aféra?

1044
01:25:01,064 --> 01:25:03,350
Ako to myslíte?

1045
01:25:04,051 --> 01:25:05,943
Hyeon Jeong...

1046
01:25:05,943 --> 01:25:10,448
O čom to hovoríte?
Aféra? Odpustenie?

1047
01:25:10,448 --> 01:25:13,343
Prečo sa vy dvaja rozprávate o takých veciach?

1048
01:25:15,353 --> 01:25:17,164
Hyeon Jeong.

1049
01:25:17,940 --> 01:25:19,924
Prepáč.

1050
01:25:19,924 --> 01:25:25,212
Ja...

1051
01:25:28,116 --> 01:25:30,060
Milujem tvoju mamu.

1052
01:25:30,060 --> 01:25:31,661
- Čože?
- Čože?

1053
01:25:34,556 --> 01:25:36,415
Hyeon Jeong, tak to nie je...

1054
01:25:36,415 --> 01:25:37,935
Počúvaj ma.

1055
01:25:37,935 --> 01:25:41,721
To preto si sa na mňa nahnevala,
keď som ti povedala o tom vyznaní?

1056
01:25:41,721 --> 01:25:43,590
Hyeon Jeong...

1057
01:25:44,399 --> 01:25:46,583
Nechutné...

1058
01:25:46,583 --> 01:25:47,969
Hyeon Jeong...

1059
01:25:47,969 --> 01:25:49,779
Hyeon Jeong!

1060
01:25:53,408 --> 01:25:58,504
Jang Pan Su, prečo si jej to povedal?!

1061
01:25:58,504 --> 01:26:01,240
No, už sa s tým nedá nič robiť.

1062
01:26:01,240 --> 01:26:04,619
A je to oveľa lepšie,
ako chodiť s vlastnou dcérou.

1063
01:26:04,619 --> 01:26:06,762
Čože?

1064
01:26:06,762 --> 01:26:08,906
Blázon!

1065
01:26:08,906 --> 01:26:14,520
Ako si jej to mohol povedať!

1066
01:26:14,520 --> 01:26:16,830
Ako vám môžem pomôcť?

1067
01:26:16,830 --> 01:26:18,557
Čo to...

1068
01:26:26,691 --> 01:26:28,985
Jang Pan Su!

1069
01:26:30,612 --> 01:26:33,348
Dnes je dobrý deň na smrť, no nie?

1070
01:26:35,883 --> 01:26:39,278
