01:27:06,105 --> 01:27:07,614
Čo?

1079
01:27:07,614 --> 01:27:09,166
Ďakujem.

1080
01:27:10,828 --> 01:27:14,505
Čože?
Ty!

1081
01:27:26,376 --> 01:27:28,260
