1103
01:28:38,056 --> 01:28:42,509
Počkať, vy ste ja?

1104
01:28:42,509 --> 01:28:47,340
Preboha, to koľko kilov som schudol?!

1105
01:28:47,340 --> 01:28:49,775
Áno, som ty!

1106
01:28:49,775 --> 01:28:51,885
Ale...

1107
01:28:51,885 --> 01:28:53,771
Si v poriadku?

1108
01:28:53,771 --> 01:28:55,481
Otec!
On je zlodej!

1109
01:28:55,481 --> 01:28:56,882
Ukradol mi moje telo!

1110
01:28:56,882 --> 01:29:00,135
Zavolaj na políciu!
Zavolaj 158!

1111
01:29:00,135 --> 01:29:01,237
Bože...

1112
01:29:01,238 --> 01:29:02,197
Prečo si ho...

1113
01:29:02,197 --> 01:29:05,800
Kvôli tebe bol v kóme,
tak prečo si ho udrel?

1114
01:29:05,800 --> 01:29:07,869
Prepáčte, môj syn mal úraz hlavy...

1115
01:29:07,869 --> 01:29:08,995
Prečo ste ma udreli?

1116
01:29:08,995 --> 01:29:11,598
Buďte obaja ticho a posaďte sa.

1117
01:29:11,598 --> 01:29:13,550
Všetko vám vysvetlím.

1118
01:29:19,764 --> 01:29:21,190
To nie je možné.

1119
01:29:21,190 --> 01:29:28,097
Takže mi chceš povedať,
že tento muž si ty a ty si ten muž?

1120
01:29:28,097 --> 01:29:29,240
Áno.

1121
01:29:29,240 --> 01:29:32,710
To budem žiť v tomto tele až do konca života?!

1122
01:29:32,710 --> 01:29:33,877
Ocko...

1123
01:29:33,877 --> 01:29:36,622
Áno, pane, čo ste hovorili?

1124
01:29:36,622 --> 01:29:40,559
Neviem, čo budeme robiť.

1125
01:29:40,559 --> 01:29:45,439
Pane, vy ste stratili tridsať rokov svojho života,
no mne tie roky pribudli.

1126
01:29:45,439 --> 01:29:47,492
Nie je to fér...

1127
01:29:47,492 --> 01:29:49,435
Fér?

1128
01:29:49,435 --> 01:29:51,012
Hej!

1129
01:29:51,012 --> 01:29:53,965
Kto zhodil všetok ten tuk?

1130
01:29:53,965 --> 01:29:55,524
- No, nie?
- Áno.

1131
01:29:55,524 --> 01:29:57,760
